{
  "stem": "25651.15",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, well, there's a transport of children from Theresienstadt to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why don't you go to Stirin and talk to Premysl Pitter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The fellow who ran it on behalf of the Ministry of Welfare-- social services in Czechoslovakia-- was a Protestant preacher called Premysl Pitter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he said, why don't you go to Prague, visit the, the chateau, and talk to Pitter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that night instead of staying in Ostrava, I took a train to Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the train was unbelievably crowded-- obviously a passenger train, but unbelievably crowded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I fought my way onto the footstep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was standing on this footstep and started moving off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I thought I can't stand on the last footstep of this train all the way to Prague, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's-- you die of exposure or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I clambered up onto the roof of the-- of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was traveling in the open air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it's rather eerie when you go through tunnels, you know, because you have to really duck because there's this wall whizzing by you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, I arrive in Prague, nicely black from soot, you know, from this journey.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And now where do you go in Prague?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I walked down the main square called Vaclavske Namesti, and there was a customer of my parent's, my father's, with whom-- whom I had met during this time in 1941 when Leo had me for a week in Prague.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found this hatter, this lady.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a sort a swanky store with women's hats, you know, height of fashion, carpets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was this dirty boy who walks in from-- straight from the station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the first idea I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked her if she remembers me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
